{"id": "ivos065", "name": "Audio_St14_702_12_29_2", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "Explosion"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Reporter A"], "content": "Wah... I don't wanna die... I don't wanna die!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Oh shut it already! Be a man and quit crying!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Reporter B"], "content": "What are you gonna do? Using our equipment without our permission... Are you... working with Simon Jackson?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Dummy. After you see this info, you'll get it. He's not the bad guy.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "Heavy Blow"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Wah! They're attacking the car... Sir, at least let us publish the truth before this gets ugly!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Reporter A"], "content": "Whatta you mean......!?\nW-W-Why should I believe you!?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "Heavy Blow"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Ugh...! Don't pay attention to them! I'm still at it! Hey! Tell me how to work this broken machine! And tell me the password!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "Heavy Blow"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Reporter B"], "content": "It's too late! This isn't a tank! We're dead!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "Heavy Blow"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunFight", "Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": ".....!?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Reporter A"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "Door Breaks"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Reporter A"], "content": "Wah! Don't kill us! I have children!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Don't worry. Get out.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "... How'd you know we were here?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "I sent him a message.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Reporter B"], "content": "You... you're working together!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "No, he saved everybody.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Reporter B"], "content": "Eh....? R-Really?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "So, are you ready to believe me or what?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Reporter A"], "content": "Th-Th-Thank, Thank you! \n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Hey, password.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Reporter A"], "content": "Of course! Here.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "I got some intel. Those buggers stopped attacking the city all of a sudden and began moving in the same direction.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Which way are they headed?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "A.R.C. headquarters. I don't know what's going on, but if what you just told us is the truth...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Yeah. It's the truth.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Switch_Off", "Unlocks Handcuffs"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "This is the last time I'm trusting you. I'm letting you go in front of everybody. This will not happen again. Go. Find Ivy and stop her. Stop all of this.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Wise decision.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Nate... thanks.\nLet's go.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "Simon.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Yeah?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "Sorry... about Pauline.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Like I said before... In the pursuit of truth, sometimes we lose what we treasure the most. \n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆発"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "うう……いやだ……死にたくない……俺は死にたくない！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "うっさいわねぇ！\n男のくせにピーピー言ってんじゃないわよ！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 B"], "content": "お前たち何をする気だ？\nうちのものを勝手に使って……\nまさかあのSimon Jacksonの仲間か？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "バカね。\nこれを見ればあんたにも分かるわ。\n彼は犯人じゃない。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "重たい衝撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "うわあ！車を攻撃してる！\n……おじさん、お願いします！\n最後に真相だけでも……みんなに知って欲しいんです！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "さっ最後だって……！？\nどうやってお前たちのことを信じろって言うんだ！？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "重たい衝撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "～っ！もういいわ！\n続けるわよ！\nこれの使い方を教えなさい！\nパスワードも！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "重たい衝撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 B"], "content": "もう無理だ！\n戦車じゃないんだぞ！\nもうここで殺されるんだ！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "重たい衝撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunFight", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "ドアを破る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "ぎゃあああ！やめてぇえ！殺さないで！\n俺には子供がいるんだ！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……もう大丈夫だ。出てこい。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……なぜこの場所が分かったの？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "僕がメッセージを送りました。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 B"], "content": "お前たち……やっぱりグルだったんだな！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "いいえ。\n皆さんを救うためです。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 B"], "content": "え……？ほ、本当に？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "どう？これで信じるしかなくなったでしょ？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "ああ！ありがとう！ありがとう！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "ほら、パスワードを寄こしなさい。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "もちろんです！\nお任せください！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "新しい情報が入った。\nやつらは急に町への襲撃をやめたらしい。\n今は一斉に同じ方向へ向かっているそうだ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "同じ方向？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "A.R.C.の本部だ。\n何が起きているのかはわからない。\nだが、もしさっきお前の言っていたことが事実なら……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あぁ、事実だ。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Switch_Off", "手錠解除"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "これが最後だ。\nお前を信じるのはこれで最後にする。\n今回は大衆の面前でお前を逃がす。\nだが、次はない。\n行け。そのIvyとかいうやつを探し出して、この災厄を止めてくれ。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "頭のいい選択だ。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Nate……ありがとう。\n行こう。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "Simon。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ん？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "Paulineのこと……悪かった。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "言っただろ……たとえ何よりも大切な物を失ったとしても、真相にたどり着いてみせるって。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆炸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "哇……我不想死……我不想死！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "吵死了！是男人就別叫了！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 B"], "content": "你們到底想幹嘛？擅自使用我們的設備……難道跟那個 Simon Jackson 也是一夥的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "白痴，看了這些資料你就懂了，他根本不是壞人。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "哇！它們在攻擊車子……大叔，拜託至少在最後讓我們把真相播報出去吧！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "最後……！？\n我、我憑什麼相信你們！？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "唔……！不管了！我要繼續！喂！告訴我這破機器怎麼用！密碼也告訴我！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 B"], "content": "來不及啦！這可不是坦克車啊！要死了！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunFight", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "破門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "哇！不要殺我！我有小孩！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……沒事了，出來吧。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……你怎麼知道我們在這裡？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "是我傳訊息給他的。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 B"], "content": "你們果然……是一夥的！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "不，是他救了大家。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 B"], "content": "咦……？真、真的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "這下你們願意相信我了吧？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "謝、謝謝！謝謝你！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "喂，密碼。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["記者 A"], "content": "當然！交給我吧。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "我收到情報了，那些傢伙突然停止對城市的攻擊，往同一個方向去了。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "同一個方向？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "A.R.C. 的總部。我不知道這是怎麼回事，不過如果你剛剛跟我說的一切都是真的的話……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯，是真的。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Switch_Off", "手銬解除"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "這是我最後一次信你了。這次當著大家的面放你走，不會再有下次了。去吧，找到那個叫 Ivy 的，阻止這一切。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "明智的判斷。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Nate……謝了。\n我們走吧。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "Simon。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "Pauline 的事……我很抱歉。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我說過了……失去最珍貴的東西也要查出真相。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "폭발"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["기자 A"], "content": "으아......죽고 싶지 않아... 죽고 싶지 않다고!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "시끄러워! 사내 놈이 징징대기는!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["기자 B"], "content": "대체 뭘 할 생각인 거야? 우리들의 장비까지 사용해서... 설마 너희들도 그 Simon Jackson과 한패?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "멍청한 녀석. 이 자료들을 보면 알게 될 거야.\n저 사람은 범인이 아니라고.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "충격"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "으아앗! 차를 공격하기 시작했어... 아저씨, 제발 마지막으로 최소한 진실만이라도 모두에게 알릴 수 있도록 도와주세요!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["기자 A"], "content": "마지막으로......! ? \n내, 내가 너희들을 뭘 믿고!?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "충격"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "큭......! 나도 몰라! 난 끝까지 할 거야! 야, 이 망가진 장비 어떻게 사용하는 건지 말해! 패스워드도!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "충격"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["기자 B"], "content": "이미 늦었어! \n이 차가 탱크인줄 알아!? 죽을 거라고!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "충격"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunFight", "총성"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......! ? \n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["기자 A"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["HeavyObj", "문을 부순다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["기자 A"], "content": "으아악! 죽이지 마세요! 제겐 아직 어린 자식이 있다고요!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......무사했군. 나와라.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "......우리가 이곳에 있는 걸 어떻게...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "제가 메시지를 보냈어요.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["기자 B"], "content": "너희들 역시... 한패로구나!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "그게 아니라... 이 사람이 모두를 구해냈다.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["기자 B"], "content": "엥......?그, 그게 진짜로...?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "이제야 내 말이 좀 믿어지냐!?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["기자 A"], "content": "가, 감사... 감사합니다!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "야, 패스워드!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["기자 A"], "content": "네! 제가 하겠습니다!\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "정보가 들어왔다. 그 녀석들 도시의 공격을 중지하고 곧바로 똑같은 방향으로 향했다는군.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "똑같은 방향?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "A.R.C.의 본부... 나도 아직 어찌된 영문이지 자세히는 모른다. 하지만 만약 네가 말해준 것들이 모두 사실이라면...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "네, 모두 사실입니다.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Switch_Off", "수갑을 풀어준다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......! \n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nate"], "content": "이번이 마지막이다. 마지막으로 딱 한 번 너를 믿어보겠다. 이번엔 모두가